{"response":{"verses":[{"auditid":"0","verse":"1","lastverse":"1","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.1","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.1","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:1","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.023.049,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.024.002,fra-LSG","text":"<h3 class=\"s\">La ruine de J\u00e9rusalem<\/h3>\n<h5 class=\"r\">V. 1-14: cf. \u00c9z 22:1-5, 14-22. 2 R 25. H\u00e9 6:8.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.24.1\" class=\"v\">1<\/sup>La neuvi\u00e8me ann\u00e9e, le dixi\u00e8me jour du dixi\u00e8me mois, la parole de l\u2019\u00c9ternel me fut adress\u00e9e, en ces mots:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.2","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:2","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.2"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.23.49","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 23:49","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.23.49"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"2","lastverse":"2","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.2","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.2","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:2","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.024.001,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.024.003,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.24.2\" class=\"v\">2<\/sup>Fils de l\u2019homme, mets par \u00e9crit la date de ce jour, de ce jour-ci! Le roi de Babylone s\u2019approche de J\u00e9rusalem en ce jour m\u00eame.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.3","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:3","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.3"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.1","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:1","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.1"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"3","lastverse":"3","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.3","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.3","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:3","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.024.002,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.024.004,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.24.3\" class=\"v\">3<\/sup>Propose une parabole \u00e0 la famille de rebelles, et dis-leur: Ainsi parle le Seigneur, l\u2019\u00c9ternel: Place, place la chaudi\u00e8re, et verses-y de l\u2019eau.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.4","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:4","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.4"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.2","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:2","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.2"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"4","lastverse":"4","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.4","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.4","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:4","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.024.003,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.024.005,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.24.4\" class=\"v\">4<\/sup>Mets-y les morceaux, tous les bons morceaux, la cuisse, l\u2019\u00e9paule; remplis-la des meilleurs os.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.5","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:5","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.5"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.3","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:3","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.3"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"5","lastverse":"5","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.5","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.5","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:5","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.024.004,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.024.006,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.24.5\" class=\"v\">5<\/sup>Choisis dans le troupeau, et entasse du bois sous la chaudi\u00e8re; fais bouillir \u00e0 gros bouillons, et que les os qui sont dedans cuisent aussi.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.6","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:6","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.6"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.4","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:4","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.4"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"6","lastverse":"6","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.6","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.6","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:6","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.024.005,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.024.007,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.24.6\" class=\"v\">6<\/sup>C\u2019est pourquoi ainsi parle le Seigneur, l\u2019\u00c9ternel: Malheur \u00e0 la ville sanguinaire, chaudi\u00e8re pleine de rouille, et dont la rouille ne se d\u00e9tache pas! Tires-en les morceaux les uns apr\u00e8s les autres, sans recourir au sort.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.7","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.7"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.5","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:5","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.5"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"7","lastverse":"7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.7","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.7","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:7","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.024.006,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.024.008,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.24.7\" class=\"v\">7<\/sup>Car le sang qu\u2019elle a vers\u00e9 est au milieu d\u2019elle; elle l\u2019a mis sur le roc nu, elle ne l\u2019a pas r\u00e9pandu sur la terre pour le couvrir de poussi\u00e8re.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.8","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:8","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.8"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.6","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:6","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.6"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"8","lastverse":"8","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.8","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.8","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:8","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.024.007,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.024.009,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.24.8\" class=\"v\">8<\/sup>Afin de montrer ma fureur, afin de me venger, j\u2019ai r\u00e9pandu son sang sur le roc nu, pour qu\u2019il ne f\u00fbt pas couvert.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.9","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:9","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.9"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.7","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:7","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.7"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"9","lastverse":"9","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.9","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.9","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:9","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.024.008,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.024.010,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.24.9\" class=\"v\">9<\/sup>C\u2019est pourquoi ainsi parle le Seigneur, l\u2019\u00c9ternel: Malheur \u00e0 la ville sanguinaire! Moi aussi je veux faire un grand b\u00fbcher.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.10","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:10","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.10"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.8","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:8","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.8"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"10","lastverse":"10","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.10","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.10","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:10","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.024.009,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.024.011,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.24.10\" class=\"v\">10<\/sup>Entasse le bois, allume le feu, cuis bien la chair, assaisonne-la, et que les os soient br\u00fbl\u00e9s.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.11","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:11","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.11"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.9","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:9","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.9"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"11","lastverse":"11","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.11","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.11","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:11","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.024.010,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.024.012,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.24.11\" class=\"v\">11<\/sup>Puis mets la chaudi\u00e8re vide sur les charbons, afin qu\u2019elle s\u2019\u00e9chauffe, que son airain devienne br\u00fblant, que sa souillure se fonde au-dedans, et que sa rouille se consume.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.12","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:12","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.12"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.10","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:10","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.10"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"12","lastverse":"12","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.12","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.12","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:12","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.024.011,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.024.013,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.24.12\" class=\"v\">12<\/sup>Les efforts sont inutiles, la rouille dont elle est pleine ne se d\u00e9tache pas; la rouille ne s\u2019en ira que par le feu.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.13","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:13","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.13"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.11","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:11","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.11"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"13","lastverse":"13","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.13","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.13","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:13","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.024.012,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.024.014,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.24.13\" class=\"v\">13<\/sup>Le crime est dans ta souillure; parce que j\u2019ai voulu te purifier et que tu n\u2019es pas devenue pure, tu ne seras plus purifi\u00e9e de ta souillure jusqu\u2019\u00e0 ce que j\u2019aie assouvi sur toi ma fureur.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.14","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:14","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.14"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.12","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:12","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.12"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"14","lastverse":"14","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.14","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.14","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:14","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.024.013,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.024.015,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.24.14\" class=\"v\">14<\/sup>Moi, l\u2019\u00c9ternel, j\u2019ai parl\u00e9; cela arrivera, et je l\u2019ex\u00e9cuterai; je ne reculerai pas, et je n\u2019aurai ni piti\u00e9 ni repentir. On te jugera selon ta conduite et selon tes actions, dit le Seigneur, l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.15","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:15","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.15"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.13","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:13","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.13"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"15","lastverse":"15","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.15","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.15","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:15","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.024.014,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.024.016,fra-LSG","text":"<h5 class=\"r\">V. 15-27: cf. J\u00e9 16:1-13.<\/h5>\n<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.24.15\" class=\"v\">15<\/sup>La parole de l\u2019\u00c9ternel me fut adress\u00e9e, en ces mots:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.16","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:16","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.16"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.14","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:14","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.14"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"16","lastverse":"16","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.16","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.16","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:16","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.024.015,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.024.017,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.24.16\" class=\"v\">16<\/sup>Fils de l\u2019homme, voici, je t\u2019enl\u00e8ve par une mort soudaine ce qui fait les d\u00e9lices de tes yeux. Tu ne te lamenteras point, tu ne pleureras point, et tes larmes ne couleront pas.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.17","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:17","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.17"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.15","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:15","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.15"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"17","lastverse":"17","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.17","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.17","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:17","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.024.016,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.024.018,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.24.17\" class=\"v\">17<\/sup>Soupire en silence, ne prends pas le deuil des morts, attache ton turban, mets ta chaussure \u00e0 tes pieds, ne te couvre pas la barbe, et ne mange pas le pain des autres.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.18","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:18","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.18"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.16","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:16","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.16"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"18","lastverse":"18","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.18","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.18","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:18","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.024.017,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.024.019,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.24.18\" class=\"v\">18<\/sup>J\u2019avais parl\u00e9 au peuple le matin, et ma femme mourut le soir. Le lendemain matin, je fis ce qui m\u2019avait \u00e9t\u00e9 ordonn\u00e9.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.19","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:19","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.19"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.17","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:17","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.17"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"19","lastverse":"19","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.19","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.19","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:19","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.024.018,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.024.020,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.24.19\" class=\"v\">19<\/sup>Le peuple me dit: Ne nous expliqueras-tu pas ce que signifie pour nous ce que tu fais?<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.20","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:20","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.20"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.18","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:18","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.18"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"20","lastverse":"20","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.20","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.20","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:20","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.024.019,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.024.021,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.24.20\" class=\"v\">20<\/sup>Je leur r\u00e9pondis: La parole de l\u2019\u00c9ternel m\u2019a \u00e9t\u00e9 adress\u00e9e, en ces mots:<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.21","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:21","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.21"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.19","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:19","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.19"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"21","lastverse":"21","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.21","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.21","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:21","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.024.020,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.024.022,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.24.21\" class=\"v\">21<\/sup>Dis \u00e0 la maison d\u2019Isra\u00ebl: Ainsi parle le Seigneur, l\u2019\u00c9ternel: Voici, je vais profaner mon sanctuaire, l\u2019orgueil de votre force, les d\u00e9lices de vos yeux, l\u2019objet de votre amour; et vos fils et vos filles que vous avez laiss\u00e9s tomberont par l\u2019\u00e9p\u00e9e.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.22","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:22","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.22"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.20","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:20","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.20"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"22","lastverse":"22","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.22","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.22","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:22","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.024.021,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.024.023,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.24.22\" class=\"v\">22<\/sup>Vous ferez alors comme j\u2019ai fait. Vous ne vous couvrirez pas la barbe, vous ne mangerez pas le pain des autres,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.23","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:23","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.23"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.21","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:21","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.21"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"23","lastverse":"23","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.23","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.23","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:23","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.024.022,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.024.024,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.24.23\" class=\"v\">23<\/sup>vous aurez vos turbans sur la t\u00eate et vos chaussures aux pieds, vous ne vous lamenterez pas et vous ne pleurerez pas; mais vous serez frapp\u00e9s de langueur pour vos iniquit\u00e9s, et vous g\u00e9mirez entre vous. \u00c9z\u00e9chiel sera pour vous un signe.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.24","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:24","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.24"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.22","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:22","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.22"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"24","lastverse":"24","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.24","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.24","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:24","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.024.023,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.024.025,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.24.24\" class=\"v\">24<\/sup>Vous ferez enti\u00e8rement comme il a fait. Et quand ces choses arriveront, vous saurez que je suis le Seigneur, l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.25","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:25","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.25"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.23","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:23","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.23"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"25","lastverse":"25","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.25","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.25","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:25","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.024.024,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.024.026,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.24.25\" class=\"v\">25<\/sup>Et toi, fils de l\u2019homme, le jour o\u00f9 je leur enl\u00e8verai ce qui fait leur force, leur joie et leur gloire, les d\u00e9lices de leurs yeux et l\u2019objet de leur amour, leurs fils et leurs filles,<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.26","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:26","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.26"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.24","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:24","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.24"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"26","lastverse":"26","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.26","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.26","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:26","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.024.025,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.024.027,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.24.26\" class=\"v\">26<\/sup>ce jour-l\u00e0 un fuyard viendra vers toi pour l\u2019annoncer \u00e0 tes oreilles.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.27","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:27","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.27"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.25","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:25","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.25"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"},{"auditid":"0","verse":"27","lastverse":"27","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.27","osis_end":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.27","label":"","reference":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:27","prev_osis_id":"Ezek.024.026,fra-LSG","next_osis_id":"Ezek.025.001,fra-LSG","text":"<p class=\"p\"><sup id=\"Ezek.24.27\" class=\"v\">27<\/sup>En ce jour, ta bouche s\u2019ouvrira avec le fuyard, et tu parleras, tu ne seras plus muet; tu seras pour eux un signe, et ils sauront que je suis l\u2019\u00c9ternel.<\/p>","parent":{"chapter":{"path":"\/chapters\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24"}},"next":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.25.1","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 25:1","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.25.1"}},"previous":{"verse":{"path":"\/verses\/fra-LSG:Ezek.24.26","name":"\u00c9z\u00e9kiel 24:26","id":"fra-LSG:Ezek.24.26"}},"copyright":"Public Domain"}],"meta":{"fums":"<script>\nvar _BAPI=_BAPI||{};\nif(typeof(_BAPI.t)==='undefined'){\ndocument.write('\\x3Cscript src=\"'+document.location.protocol+'\/\/d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js\"\\x3E\\x3C\/script\\x3E');}\ndocument.write(\"\\x3Cscript\\x3E_BAPI.t('5af81fc24294a7.68731267');\\x3C\/script\\x3E\");\n<\/script><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fc24294a7.68731267\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/><\/noscript>","fums_tid":"5af81fc24294a7.68731267","fums_js_include":"d2ue49q0mum86x.cloudfront.net\/include\/fums.c.js","fums_js":"var _BAPI=_BAPI||{};if(typeof(_BAPI.t)!='undefined'){ _BAPI.t('5af81fc24294a7.68731267'); }","fums_noscript":"<img src=\"https:\/\/d3a2okcloueqyx.cloudfront.net\/nf1?t=5af81fc24294a7.68731267\" height=\"1\" width=\"1\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" style=\"height: 0; width: 0;\" \/>"}}}